attributes.name: Frosted Sunset
attributes.body: Frosted Sunset is a heavy indica dominant hybrid that is a delicious child strain from two powerful parent strains, Sunset Sherbet and Chocolate Frosting. Its buds tend to be spade shaped, bright yellow, with dark purple and lime-green highlights. It has vibrant orange pistils that spider around and through the buds which are caked with a heavy frosting of milky trichomes, further adding to its yellow appearance.
